main event: A military report documents a UFO sighting over SE Guam on December 19, 1960.
interesting points: The observation lasted for 15 minutes,The sighting involved one object that followed a course of 260 degrees,Characteristics of the object suggested it might be a satellite,The object was observed in clear skies with clouds at a 13-degree elevation,The UFO disappeared from sight after flashing brightly while moving slowly.
witness description: no human faces or witnesses recorded in the report
